s-adjusted-up-bones-adjusted-down/79682 |archivedate=June 14, 2011 |url-status=dead |df=}}</ref>\n| end3              = {{End date|2011|5|19}}\n| endrating3        = 3.72<ref name=\"ratings1905\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/20/thursday-final-ratings-american-idol-big-bang-the-office-greys-mentalist-adjusted-up/93470/ |title=Thursday Final Ratings: 'American Idol,' 'Big Bang,' 'The Office,' 'Grey's,' 'Mentalist' Adjusted Up |publisher=[[TV by the Numbers]] |last=Seidman |first=Robert |date=May 20, 2011 |accessdate=May 21, 2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5zQN25FWt?url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/05/20/thursday-final-ratings-american-idol-big-bang-the-office-greys-mentalist-adjusted-up/93470 |archivedate=June 14, 2011 |url-status=dead |df=}}</ref>\n| season3           = 2010\u201311\n| rank3             = 116<ref name=\"1011ratings\" />\n| viewers3          = 5.1<ref name=\"1011ratings\" />\n\n| link4             = Parks and Recreation (season 4)\n| timeslot4         = Thursday 8:30 pm {{small|(1\u201310)}}<br />Thursday 9:30 pm {{small|(11\u201322)}}\n| episodes4         = 22\n| start4            = {{Start date|2011|9|22}}\n| startrating4      = 4.11<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/09/23/thursday-finals-big-bang-theory-the-x-factor-parks-recreation-and-whitney-adjusted-up/104707/|title=Thursday Finals: 'Big Bang Theory,' 'The X Factor,' 'Parks & Recreation' and 'Whitney' Adjusted Up|work=TV by the Numbers|last=Seidman|first=Robert|date=September 23, 2011|accessdate=September 24, 2011|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68VAJjfOG?url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/09/23/thursday-finals-big-bang-theory-the-x-factor-parks-recreation-and-whitney-adjusted-up/104707/|archive-date=June 18, 2012|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| end4              = {{End date|2012|5|10}}\n| endrating4        = 3.42<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/05/11/thursday-final-ratings-big-bang-theor